snippet.title: OBSERVER Teaser Trailer (Edge of the Earth)
snippet.description:
OBSER∇ER is a cryptic, minimalistic first person adventure game being developed by AeroJoust, a multinational duo of game developers. 

Heavily inspired by Myst and the games of Fumito Ueda.
